article_id:2365,category_name:News,title_name:Issues in the Rhythmic Resolutions facility revival event,image_path:,message:<div>The following issues were occurring in the Rhythmic Resolutions facility revival event that started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626328800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Claiming endeavor rewards from certain limited endeavors after completing them resulted in an error, taking players back to the title screen.</div><div>・After certain limited endeavors were completed and their rewards claimed, said endeavors reappeared in the endeavors list.</div><div>・Even after certain limited endeavors were fully completed, the &quot;Clear&quot; tag didn&#39;t display, and obtaining the rewards was impossible even by using the &quot;Accept All&quot; button.</div><div><br></div><div>■Affected players</div><div>All players who participated in this event between approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626328800"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626329400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>These issues were addressed around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626339720"></span>, but it may take some time for the fixes to be applied.<br><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1626340500,update_time1626413019